caption: The new probe for transport measurement in the dilution refrigerator is up! This is a year-long work for me. Thanks my grad student Ludwig for advice and help, I managed to design and assemble the whole new probe, including the mechanical parts and PCBs. The new probe has RC/RF filters and golden meander to lower the electron temperature below 30 mK. Really appreciate it works so well!
